# Conventional Commits

Follow the **Conventional Commits** section in the repository root **`AGENTS.md`** for subject format, allowed types, breaking changes, examples, and anti-patterns.

- Subjects in **English**, **imperative** mood, per [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/).
- Installer commits are linted with **`@commitlint/config-conventional`** — see `installer/commitlint.config.cjs`.
